  "title": "Relationship Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>[Job ID: 401667]</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Overview</strong></p>\n<p>Are you a<strong> </strong>highly motivated sales-driven individual for your next challenge? This renowned international bank is looking for Relationship Managers to join their growing team as part of their expansion plans.</p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Conduct professional, consultative financial analysis and profiling sessions to address customers’ financial needs and objectives.</li>\n  <li>Build and strengthen customer relationships by providing regular updates on market trends and insights into local and international financial products.</li>\n  <li>Promote and offer a wide variety of banking products to existing and potential clients, including structured notes, leveraged FX trades, corporate and sovereign bonds, etc.</li>\n  <li>Deliver expert financial analysis and customized wealth management solutions, such as bancassurance, loans, and investment products.</li>\n  <li>Participate actively in branch activities, supporting the overall success of the bank.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Diploma in any discipline</strong></li>\n  <li>Results-oriented, dynamic, and self-driven</li>\n  <li><strong>Very keen in a sales-fronting role.</strong></li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills are crucial for building strong client relationships.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. However, rest assured that all applications will be updated to our resume bank for future opportunities.<br>\n<br>\nPlease kindly refer to the Privacy Policy of Good Job Creations for your reference: https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/<br>\n<br>\nEA Personnel Name: Ong Kang Quan Ryan<br>\nEA Personnel Registration Number: R23116952<br>\nEA License No.: 07C5771</p>",
